OL,3,COfficer accused of Kaba murder thought
OL,4,Ccolleague was 'about to die', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police firearms officer
OL,8,FMartyn Blake, who is charged with the
OL,9,Fmurder of Chris Kaba in September
OL,10,F2022, has told a jury he pulled the
OL,11,Ftrigger because he thought one of his
OL,12,Fcolleagues "would be dead" and felt a
OL,13,Fduty to protect them.
OL,15,FBlake denies murdering 24-year-old
OL,16,FChris Kaba who was shot in the head
OL,17,Fduring an armed police operation in
OL,18,FStreatham, south London, two years ago.
