OL,7,FGiving evidence in public for the
OL,8,Ffirst time at the Old Bailey on
OL,9,FMonday, Martyn Blake said he was
OL,10,F"filled with dread" as the Audi Mr
OL,11,FKaba was driving moved backwards and
OL,12,Fforwards with police officers
OL,13,Fsurrounding the car.
