OL,3,COfficer accused of Kaba murder thought
OL,4,Ccolleague was 'about to die', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Blake fatally shot Mr Kaba through
OL,8,Fthe windscreen of the Audi in
OL,9,FStreatham, south-east London on
OL,10,FSeptember 5, 2022.
OL,12,FThe court has already heard that when
OL,13,Fhemmed in by police cars, Mr Kaba,
OL,14,Ftried to ram his way past, between a
OL,15,Fmarked police car and a Tesla parked
OL,16,Fnearby. Mr Blake is accused of murder,
OL,17,Fwhich he denies.
