OL,3,COfficer accused of Kaba murder thought
OL,4,Ccolleague was 'about to die', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe told the jury he could hear wheel-
OL,8,Fspinning and the car's engine revving
OL,9,Fas armed officers tried to get Mr Kaba
OL,10,Fto get out of the car. Mr Blake was
OL,11,Fasked by his barrister Patrick Gibbs
OL,12,FKC why he had opened fire.
OL,14,FHe said: "I had a genuine belief that
OL,15,Fthere was an imminent threat to life,
OL,16,FI thought one or more of my colleagues
OL,17,Fwas about to die.
